(106, '<div id=\"base-container\">\r\n<div id=\"content\" class=\"elements\">\r\n<div class=\"container section\">\r\n<div class=\"full-width column\">\r\n<h1 class=\"nobg elements\">Reynold\'s Clothing</h1>\r\n<div class=\"container section\">\r\n<div class=\"full-width column\">\r\n<p>Reynold\'s Clothing has provided Denison and West Central Iowa quality men\'s wear for over 45 years.</p>\r\n<p>Reynold\'s Clothing is a second generation family owned and operated business.  Since 1972 Reynold\'s Clothing has provided generations of customers quality merchandise with personalized customer service.  Over 8,000 square feet of sales space lets us offer great brands such as Under Armour, Carhartt, Red Wing,   Silver Denim, Big Star, Lucky Brand, Nautica, FX Fusion, Van Heusen, Haggar, Keen Utility, Merrell, Clarks, Florsheim, Jockey, Gold Toe and many more trusted names.</p>\r\n<p>Reynold\'s sells everything from boots to suits. Located in the heart of downtown Denison, our friendly and knowledgeable staff looks forward to helping you look your best. Reynold\'s Clothing is \"a hometown clothing store.\"</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container section\">\r\n<div class=\"one-third column hp-3ads\"><a href=\"http://www.reynoldsclothing.com/casual.asp\"><img src=\"http://www.reynoldsclothing.com/uploads/hp-casual.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\r\n<h2>Casual</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-third column hp-3ads\"><a href=\"http://www.reynoldsclothing.com/dress.asp\"><img src=\"http://www.reynoldsclothing.com/uploads/hp-dress-formal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\r\n<h2>Dress & Formal</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-third column hp-3ads last\"><a href=\"http://www.reynoldsclothing.com/work.asp\"><img src=\"http://www.reynoldsclothing.com/uploads/hp-workandboots.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\r\n<h2>Work Wear & Boots</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"footer\">\r\n<div class=\"container section\">\r\n<div class=\"half column\">\r\n<p><strong>Reynold\'s