D which secures private data in apps for added protection.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_3jmfs-\">\r\n<div class=\"_3-fMoP _2briKY\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Pk2voS _2XGBfy Lib_as\"><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/j16qm4w0/tablet/f/h/g/apple-mp1j2hn-a-original-imaest9wgguy88re.jpeg?q=90\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"><strong>Cameras</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"DQKXPi\">\r\n<p>Capture the world around you with stunning clarity and sharpness with iPad’s 8 MP camera. Record 1080p HD videos of events that you want to keep replaying and edit them directly on this iPad. With its front-facing 1.2 MP FaceTime HD camera, you can video call your friends and family from all over the world.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_3jmfs-\">\r\n<div class=\"_3-fMoP _2briKY\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Pk2voS _2XGBfy Lib_as\"><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/j16qm4w0/tablet/f/h/g/apple-mp1j2hn-a-original-imaest9wfycfzhxr.jpeg?q=90\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"><strong>Continuity</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"DQKXPi\">\r\n<p>Start something on this iPad and complete it on either your iPhone or Mac. You can also use AirDrop to transfer and share files between devices.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_3jmfs-\">\r\n<div class=\"_3-fMoP _2briKY\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Pk2voS _2XGBfy Lib_as\"><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/j16qm4w0/tablet/f/h/g/apple-mp1j2hn-a-original-imaest9wverbtdh8.jpeg?q=90\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"><strong>Design</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"DQKXPi\">\r\n<p>The aluminium unibody construction of this iPad ensures durability and reassures a solid feel. This tablet also weighs just about 478 g and is just 7.5 mm thin.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_3jmfs-\">\r\n<div class=\"_3-fMoP _2briKY\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Pk2voS _2XGBfy Lib_as\"><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/j16qm4w0/tablet/f/h/g/apple-mp1j2hn-a-original-imaest9wverbtdh8.jpeg?q=90\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"><strong>Speedy Surfing and Streaming</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"DQKXPi\">\r\n<p>Stay connected all the time, wherever you are as this iPad supports up to 150 Mbps 4G LTE and up to 866 Mbps Wifi for speedy surfing and streaming.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Product Description\r\nThe Apple iPad packs quite a punch and gives you an incredible display and comes with over a million of apps so you can do what you love to do.\r\n\r\nRetina Display\r\nWhether you’re browsing the internet, shopping, looking at family vacation photos, working on a presentation or watching a movie, the Apple iPad’s 24.63 cm (9.7) Retina display, along with 2048x1536 resolution, brings it all to life to give you an immersive viewing experience.', 4, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med/1505278756_1.png', 1, 1, 1, 36, 0, 1, '2017-09-07 05:20:56', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
