(256, 'hospital Services', '20000.00', 'item', 'Service', '<h1 class=\"articleTitle\">Hospital Reception Information:</h1>\r\n<p><strong>On Admission:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"http://rumourhasit.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/life-kingsbury-hospital-reception-5.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for hospital reception\" width=\"367\" height=\"246\"></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>The reception counter is one of the most important areas of the hospital and the same is true at Civil Hospital. Upon arrival at Civil Hospital, visitors to the hospital require help vis-à-vis information regarding location of various services and facilities. The reception acts as the first line of contact to provide the necessary help to the patients and their attendants through reception counter and ‘MAY I HELP YOU’ desks.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Functions:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>        Reception acts as the first line of guidance for patients visiting Civil Hospital.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Guide the patients and their attendants regarding location and timings of OPD clinics, laboratories, wards and departments.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Attend to all telephonic enquiries regarding information concerning the patients, the doctors and clinics and OPD schedule.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h1 class=\"articleTitle\"> Operating Theatre:</h1>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"http://www.innovations-report.com/upload_waf/hochpraezisions-op_618073.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for operating theatre\" width=\"346\" height=\"231\"></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong><strong>An operating theater (also known as an operating room, operating suite, operation theatre or operation suite) is a facility within a </strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital\"><strong>hospital</strong></a><strong> where surgical operations are carried out in a </strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asepsis\"><strong>sterile</strong></a><strong> environment.</strong></p>\r\n<h1 class=\"articleTitle\">Operating Rooms</h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"articleTitle\">  <img src=\"http://www.wohlsenconstruction.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/healthcare-construction-phoenixville-hospital-operating-room-expansion-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for operating rooms\" width=\"355\" height=\"237\"></h1>\r\n<p><strong>Operating rooms are spacious, easy to clean, and well-lit, typically with overhead </strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgical_lighting\"><strong>surgical lights</strong></a><strong>, and may have viewing screens and </strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_monitor\"><strong>monitors</strong></a><strong>. Operating rooms are generally windowless and feature controlled temperature and humidity. Special air handlers filter the air and maintain a slightly elevated pressure. Electricity support has backup systems in case of a black-out. Rooms are supplied with wall suction, oxygen, and possibly other anesthetic gases.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Surgeon and assistants:</strong></p>\r\n<h1 class=\"articleTitle\"><strong>Surgeon and assistants:</strong></h1>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSWIeB1qwDr8UHzwpqUbNmu7NUmNNA5WeAaxV8HDiIGYT1WkUjMgw\" alt=\"Image result for surgeons of hospitals\" width=\"230\" height=\"144\"><img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT37opXAmNvK3-bcZ4UuzlfGtUv5aHTP2CNrpcNKTfC7RHUmJ5-aw\" alt=\"Image result for surgeons of hospitals\" width=\"262\" height=\"138\"></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Early operating theatres in an educational setting have had raised tables or chairs at the center for performing operations surrounded by several rows of seats for students and other spectators to observe the case in progress. The surgeons wore street clothes with an </strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apron\"><strong>apron</strong></a><strong> to protect them from blood stains, and they operated bare-handed with </strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sterilization_(microbiology)\"><strong>unsterilized</strong></a><strong> instruments and supplies</strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'Location and Timings: The Civil Hospital has reception counters to provide all possible help and information to the patients visiting as well as to cater to the telephonic enquiries. Functions: ... Guide the patients and their attendants regarding location and timings of OPD clinics, laboratories, wards and departments.May 21, 2014\r\nReception | Civil Hospital Amdavad', 5, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 1, 122, 0, 3, '2017-09-14 06:45:36', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
(257, 'water skiing', '3000.00', '', 'Service', '<div class=\"hide-on-mobile\"><header class=\"content__head tonal__head tonal__head--tone-news\r\n    \r\n    \">\r\n<div class=\"content__header tonal__header\">\r\n<div class=\"gs-container\">\r\n<div class=\"content__main-column u-cf\">\r\n<h1 class=\"content__headline\">Top 10 water sports and activities in Tobago</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tonal__standfirst u-cf\">\r\n<div class=\"gs-container\">\r\n<div class=\"content__main-column\">\r\n<div class=\"content__standfirst\" data-link-name=\"standfirst\" data-component=\"standfirst\">Life in Tobago revolves around the gorgeous warm water of the Caribbean, and a host of sports and activities around the island take full adavantage of it</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header></div>\r\n<div class=\"content__main tonal__main tonal__main--tone-news\">\r\n<div class=\"gs-container\">\r\n<div class=\"content__main-column content__main-column--article js-content-main-column \">\r\n<div class=\"js-score\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"js-sport-tabs football-tabs content__mobile-full-width\"> </div>\r\n<figure class=\"media-primary media-content()  \" data-component=\"image\" data-media-id=\"gu-image-418654348\">\r\n<div class=\"u-responsive-ratio\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/static/sys-images/Travel/Pix/pictures/2013/9/25/1380124880896/Sailing-Catamaran-off-the-010.jpg?w=620&q=20&auto=format&usm=12&fit=max&dpr=2&s=5b20abb8c9abcbad255b716e1254f0ca 1240w\" media=\"(min-width: 980px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 980px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"620px\"><source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/static/sys-images/Travel/Pix/pictures/2013/9/25/1380124880896/Sailing-Catamaran-off-the-010.jpg?w=620&q=55&auto=format&usm=12&fit=max&s=a876de1412d52d977f3065ec6d73a7fb 620w\" media=\"(min-width: 980px)\" sizes=\"620px\"><source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/static/sys-images/Travel/Pix/picture