 performs everyday tasks like checking your calendar, replying to text messages, and staying connected in an instant.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_3jmfs-\">\r\n<div class=\"_3-fMoP _2briKY\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"Pk2voS _2XGBfy Lib_as\"><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/smartwatch/a/8/s/mp022hn-a-apple-original-imaemy6y3dp5uktm.jpeg?q=90\"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"_1GuuTl\"><strong><span xss=removed>Track and Share your Activity</span></strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"DQKXPi\">\r\n<p>Isn’t it wonderful to know that your hard work is showing good results? With this smartwatch, you can see how active you are as it shows you details of how many steps you take in a day or any indoor and outdoor activities that you take part in a day, and how much more you need to exercise to stay fit. You can also share and compare your Activity rings with your friends to motivate each other or compete with each other to stay fit.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Keep a track of the number of steps you take and the calories you burn, set your workout goals, monitor your heart rate and stress levels, and also stay connected via calls and messages by simply strapping the Apple Watch Series 1. Do all of this faster than ever as this smartwatch is powered by a dual-core processor.\r\n\r\nAddition Details: This device\'s battery life lasts for up to 18 hours, including 45 minutes of using apps and a 30?minute workout with music playback, and checking time and notifications 90 times each. The battery life may vary based on usage. The Apple Watch app is required to use this device\'s smart functions.\r\n \r\nProduct Description\r\nHow wonderful would it be if you could track your daily activity, monitor your health, stay connected to people, and do much more with just one device? All this is possible with the Apple Watch Series 1, thanks to its dual-