(309, 'fast tranportetion  by truck', '5000.00', '', 'Service', '<div class=\"vortalMarketingContent-col\">\r\n<p>uShip\'s unique online transportation marketplace connects you to an extensive network of truck transporters. Start by taking a look at previous truck transport transactions on our <a href=\"https://www.uship.com/cost-to-ship/heavy-equipment/trucks/\">cost to ship a truck</a> page. There you will be able to get more familiar with the uShip process and then proceed through your listing with confidence.</p>\r\n<p>Simply post the details of your truck transport job- including type of truck, pickup and delivery details, time frame and budget restrictions. Once your shipment is live in our marketplace you will receive bids from customer-rated truck transport companies. Be sure to read through their profiles; which include business information, insurance coverage and feedback from previous customers, so you feel comfortable accepting the bid that works best for you.</p>\r\n<h1>Truck Shipping Made Easy</h1>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.easyhaul.com/\">EasyHaul</a> has many years of experience shipping mid-sized and heavy trucks. We’re experts at shipping salvage trucks that may not run, as well as shipping trucks in perfect condition. Our experts select the most suitable transportation method and process according to the weight and size of your vehicle.</p>\r\n<p>We have relationships with reputable shipping companies and freight forwarders. This enables us to use a wide variety of shipping methods, including: flatbeds, low-boy trailers, vessel trailers, multi-axle extendable step deck trailers, and enclosed shipping. We make sure our customers understand their options and meet their needs with the best solution.</p>\r\n<h2>Shipping Trucks Reliably</h2>\r\n<p>All trucks we ship are insured as part of our guaranteed quote. EasyHaul only uses qualified and bonded drivers. Every company and driver we use is approved and licensed by the U.S. Department of Transportation Federal Motor Carrier Safety Administration.</p>\r\n<p>As a one-stop-destination for all your truck shipping needs, EasyHaul gives you the convenience of scheduling either pickup or delivery to your doorstep. We can pick-up at auction yards and deliver wherever you want. Even if your neighborhood bans oversized vehicles, our experts look for the nearest alternative delivery location.</p>\r\n<h2>Text and Email Updates Sent to You at All Points</h2>\r\n<p>Our modern tracking system automatically sends you text messages and/or email updates at every step of the delivery process. You can also access your account to see the full history of shipping activity. Our custom tracking system is easy to understand and operate. You can find the status on any shipment at anytime.</p>\r\n<h2>More Benefits of EasyHaul Truck Shipping Services</h2>\r\n<h3>Salvage Shipping Specialists</h3>\r\n<p>We have shipped thousands of trucks across the U.S. Our specialty is shipping salvage trucks. Many companies won’t take these, but we’ll get them to you wherever you want. We are the premier salvage truck shipping company and will pick-up your rig at any salvage or auction yard.</p>\r\n<h3>Experienced Professionals</h3>\r\n<p>Our shipping agents are dedicated employees and have been with us for years. At EasyHaul we take special care to ensure that every customer is completely satisfied with our services. Our agents know all the ins-and-outs of shipping so that you don’t have to. They’re the ones who make it easy for you.</p>\r\n<h3>Door-to-Door Shipping</h3>\r\n<p>As a full-service provider for all your truck shipping needs, EasyHaul gives you the convenience of scheduling either pickup or delivery to your doorstep. Once you place an order all you need to do it take it easy. We’ll do the rest.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"vortalMarketingContent-col\"> </div>', 'uShip\'s unique online transportation marketplace connects you to an extensive network of truck transporters. Start by taking a look at previous truck transport transactions on our cost to ship a truck page. There you will be able to get more familiar with the uShip process and then proceed through your listing with confidence.\r\n\r\nSimply post the details of your truck transport job- including type of truck, pickup and delivery details, time frame and budget restrictions. Once your shipment is live in our marketplace you will receive bids from customer-rated truck transport companies.', 0, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 1, 171, 0, 65, '2017-09-28 12:22:07', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
(310, 'aadhar card', '500.00', '', 'Service', '<h1>Aadhaar Card</h1>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://eaadharcarduidai.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/aadhar-card-logo-eng-2-new.png\" alt=\"E-Aadhar Card |www.uidai.gov.in| Resident.uidai.net.in-Help Portal\"></p>\r\n<p>Before Aadhaar Card ,We have to carry different types of <strong>Identification</strong> and <strong>Address.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Proof</strong> <strong>Documents</strong> : </p>\r\n<p>1)Ration Card </p>\r\n<p>2)Pan Card</p>\r\n<p>3)Electricity Bill </p>\r\n<p>4)Water Bill</p>\r\n<p>5)Telephone Bill </p>\r\n<p>6)Voter Card </p>\r\n<p>It was a monotonous task to Show different Documents at different Places.</p>\r\n<p>This Problem is Solved by Aadhaar Card and Now You can <strong>Use Aadhar card Both as an Address Proof and an  Identity Proof Documents</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>UID – Unique Identification</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>AADHAR  – 12 Digit Uid Card</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>NPR – National Population Register</strong></p>', 'Many countries around the world use a unique identity system whereby each citizen receives a number that hold all details pertinent to their identity under it. The government of India has also sought such a system India and have called it Aadhaar, which is also referred to as UID. They then intend to use this number to provide benefits to the citizens through the Aadhaar number. These benefits could include things like various subsidies that the government provides, include things like the subsidy on gas. The project is run by the Unique Identification Authority of India (UIDAI) and was introduced in January 2009. The project has faced some problems since its inception with claims being made that the project was not constitutionally sound as it involved the collection of biometric data of the citizens by the government.', 0, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 0, 172, 0, 62, '2017-09-29 05:29:06', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
(311, 'pan card', '400.00', '', 'Service', '<h2><img src=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/media/logo.png\" alt=\"ApplyPanIndia.in\"></h2>\r\n<h2>Your Pan Card for in Simple Steps</h2>\r\n<h2><strong xss=removed>1.</strong><span xss=removed> Fill the Online PAN Card Application</span></h2>\r\n<div class=\"text-pos\">\r\n<p><strong>2.</strong> Make Payment Online<br><strong>3.</strong> Print & Sign the Documents<br><strong>4.</strong> Send the Docs by post/courier</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"alt\">Apply Online For PAN Card</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/form49a.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"img-border\"><img src=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/media/apply-for-new-pan.jpg\" alt=\"apply for New PAN Card\"></span></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Apply for a new PAN card. This online process is for Individuals, who are Indian citizen, before applying for a new PAN card make sure that you don\'t have PAN card or PAN number.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"tick\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>In case you lost your PAN card and have the PAN number <a href=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/application-for-lost-pan-card.php\"><strong>apply for lost PAN card</strong></a>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>In case you want to make any changes in your PAN card then <strong><a href=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/application-for-updation-pan-card.php\">apply for changes in PAN card</a></strong> (like name, father\'s name, Date of birth).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'PAN Card is an essential document for most of us in India, not just for the purpose of filing tax returns, but many of us, use it as a form of identification, as well. Today having a PAN card has become mandatory for most people irrespective of whether they have taxable income or not.', 0, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 0, 172, 0, 62, '2017-09-29 05:35:54', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
(312, 'PAN CARD', '400.00', '', 'Service', '<h2><img src=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/media/logo.png\" alt=\"ApplyPanIndia.in\"></h2>\r\n<h2>Your Pan Card for in Simple Steps</h2>\r\n<h2><strong xss=removed>1.</strong><span xss=removed> Fill the Online PAN Card Application</span></h2>\r\n<div class=\"text-pos\">\r\n<p><strong>2.</strong> Make Payment Online<br><strong>3.</strong> Print & Sign the Documents<br><strong>4.</strong> Send the Docs by post/courier</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"alt\">Apply Online For PAN Card</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/form49a.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"img-border\"><img src=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/media/apply-for-new-pan.jpg\" alt=\"apply for New PAN Card\"></span></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Apply for a new PAN card. This online process is for Individuals, who are Indian citizen, before applying for a new PAN card make sure that you don\'t have PAN card or PAN number.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"tick\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p>In case you lost your PAN card and have the PAN number <a href=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/application-for-lost-pan-card.php\"><strong>apply for lost PAN card</strong></a>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>In case you want to make any changes in your PAN card then <strong><a href=\"https://www.applypanindia.in/application-for-updation-pan-card.php\">apply for changes in PAN card</a></strong> (like name, father\'s name, Date of birth).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'PAN Card is an essential document for most of us in India, not just for the purpose of filing tax returns, but many of us, use it as a form of identification, as well. Today having a PAN card has become mandatory for most people irrespective of whether they have taxable income or not.', 0, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 1, 172, 0, 62, '2017-09-29 05:37:11', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
(313, 'SERVICES OF E SEVA', '500.00', '', 'Service', '<p><img src=\"https://www.mahaonline.gov.in/Images/logo-mr.png\" alt=\"MahaOnline Logo\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>As per the Government website, the requirements to open a CSC or Maha e-Seva Kendra, as a Village Level Entrepreneur (VLE) are:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>a) They should have a valid Aadhaar number.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>b) The VLE should be a village youth above 18 years of age.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>c) The VLE must have passed the 10th level examination from a recognized board as minimum level of educational qualification.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>d) The VLE should be fluent in reading and writing the local dialect and should also have basic level knowledge of English language.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>e) Prior knowledge in basic computer skills would be a preferred advantage.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>f) The VLE should be motivated enough to be a prime driver of social change and disperse his/her duties with utmost dedication and honesty.</strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'Under the National e-Governance plan formulated by the Central Government, Common Service Centers Scheme (CSC), known in Maharashtra as the Maha e-Seva Kendras, have been set up, run by authorized private individuals to enable easy access of citizens to various government and private sector services.\r\n\r\n ', 0, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 1, 172, 0, 62, '2017-09-29 06:38:06', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
(314, 'Trading Services', '500.00', '', 'Service', '<h1 class=\"rstotle\"><span class=\"item\"><span class=\"fn\">Ambika Traders</span> </span></h1>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://4.imimg.com/data4/UK/AG/GLADMIN-16331630/2-250x250.png\" alt=\"Image result for trading about oils and kirana\"></p>\r\n<p><strong>Trade</strong> involves the transfer of <a title=\"Goods and services\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Goods_and_services\">goods or services</a> from one person or entity to another, often in exchange for money. A network that allows trade is called a <a title=\"Market (economics)\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Market_(economics)\">market</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The original form of trade, <a title=\"Barter\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barter\">barter</a>, saw the direct exchange of goods and services for other goods and services.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Samuelson1939_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trade#cite_note-Samuelson1939-1\">[1]</a></sup> Barter is trading things without the use of money.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Samuelson1939_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trade#cite_note-Samuelson1939-1\">[1]</a></sup> Later one side of the barter started to involve precious metals, which gained</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://4.imimg.com/data4/SC/QY/GLADMIN-16331630/cdeerrr-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for trading about oils and kirana\">symbolic as well as practical importance. Modern traders generally negotiate through a medium of exchange, such as money. As a result, <strong>buying</strong>can be separated from <strong>selling</strong>, or <a title=\"Earnings\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Earnings\">earning</a>. The <a title=\"History of money\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_money#The_emergence_of_money\">invention of money</a> (and later <a title=\"Credit (finance)\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Credit_(finance)\">credit</a>, <a class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paper money\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paper_money\">paper money</a> and <a title=\"Digital currency\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_currency\">non-physical money</a>) greatly simplified and promoted trade. Trade between two traders is called bilateral trade, while trade between more than two traders is called multilateral trade.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://3.imimg.com/data3/TF/IP/MY-11448765/miscellaneous-kirana-items-500x500.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for trading about oils and kirana\" width=\"236\" height=\"234\"></p>\r\n<p>Trade exists due to the specialization and division of labor, in which most people concentrate on a small aspect of production, but use that output in trades for other products and needs.<sup id=\"cite_ref-DollarKraay2004_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trade#cite_note-DollarKraay2004-2\">[2]</a></sup> Trade exists between regions because different regions may have a <a title=\"Comparative advantage\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparative_advantage\">comparative advantage</a> (perceived or real) in the </p>', 'We\'re hiringCustomer careFree ListingAdvertiseAbout usMediaTestimonialsFeedbackBusiness Badge\r\nMeals on Train /Order Flowers /Order Food Online /Book a table /Shop Online /Order Books /Movies /Entertainment /Grocery Shopping /Chemists /Laundry Pick Up /Courier Pick Up /Doctors /Bills & Recharge /Insurance /AC Repair /Flights /Bus /Train /Hotels /International Sim /Cab & Car Rental /Spa & Salon /Car service /Water Purifier Service /Hospitals /Lab Test /Jobs /Automobile /On Demand Service', 0, 0, 0.00, '//www.bigmee.com/dist/img/products/med///', 1, 1, 1, 173, 0, 29, '2017-09-29 08:36:50', '2017-10-06 21:54:47'),
